## How to refresh this evidence

```bash
# 1. Run the device STIG roles (dry-run is enough to produce artifacts)
ansible-playbook cisco/roles/cisco_nxos_stig/playbooks/run.yml -i inventory
ansible-playbook cisco/roles/cisco_asa_stig/playbooks/run.yml -i inventory
# ...etc for each device class

# 2. Regenerate this consolidated package
ansible-playbook network_policy/roles/ndm_srg_assessment/playbooks/run.yml
```
